{"tid":1578632,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"fresh grad既我們爭氣點好嗎？","createTime":"2019-09-18T08:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T09:24:24.000Z","uid":255501,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aeefc74d6e25e5e4356e0166e21991cc11c8f755","tid":1578632,"uid":255501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:08:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Up9-C4_8dVo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUp9-C4_8dVo&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=cb4fbf7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Up9-C4_8dVo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以下呢番說話，我想同一眾覺得自己under pay同埋不甘於現況既<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">fresh grad</span>講：</span><br />\n<br />\n你地每一位都比自己想像之中強大，吾好妄自菲薄睇小自己。馬雲都系考左3次高考先入到u，畢左業kfc都吾請，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你地既起步點一點都不低！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nFresh grad既你地究境做緊咩野？拎一份萬幾蚊既人工幫老細搵錢？定真系真心享受呢份工作？仲記吾記得<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">細個既自己系想成為一個點既人呢？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n吾好覺得番工就無風險，吾好比自己停落尼，不斷裝備自己。到有機會尼既時候先能夠把握到，機會系留比有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好準備</span></span>同埋<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敢去冒風險</span></span>既人。<br />\n<br />\n覺得老細比你既人工under paid既話，努力啦！無野輸架！我地由細到大比人教導要成功，卻讓我們<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">害怕失敗、害怕未知</span></span>的東西。<br />\n<br />\n呢個更系香港教育既失敗，因為呢個制度要培育既系幫社會run system既人，而不是具<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">創新力、變通</span></span>既新生代。<br />\n<br />\n點解吾去發揮自己擅長既領域，去創業！就算輸左創業既錢，但你地賺既<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">系寶貴經驗</span></span>。再來阿，愈年輕承受既風險應該愈大。"},{"pid":"e4db970a24d6969e23c2a52846cd1858c209823f","tid":1578632,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:09:09.000Z","msg":"922和你shop和你suck<br />\n924 各區放映<br />\n928民陣<br />\n929全球抗赤納粹<br />\n101國殤日"},{"pid":"2b